.TH "KWM" "1" "2026-03-31" "kwm" "kewuaa's window manager"
.PP
.SH NAME
.PP
kwm - kewuaa'\&s window manager for River Wayland compositor
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBkwm\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.br
\fBriver\fR -c kwm
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
\fIRiver\fR is a non-monolithic Wayland compositor, it does not combine the compositor
and window manager into one program.\&
.PP
kwm is a DWM-like dynamic tiling window manager implementing the
river-window-management-v1 protocol.\&
.PP
See the default configuration file for detailed features.\&
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB-h,-help\fR
.RS 4
Print a help message and exit.\&
.PP
.RE
\fB-v,-version\fR
.RS 4
Print the version number and exit.\&
.PP
.RE
\fB-c,-config\fR
.RS 4
Specify custom configuration file path.\&
.PP
.PP
.RE
.SH KEYBINDINGS
.PP
kwm supports separate keybindings for each mode.\& Modes can be customized in the
configuration file.\&
.PP
